---
title: Roast Cauliflower Biryani with Currants, Roasted Almonds & Yoghurt
description: Curry on rice is all well and good, but when the rice itself is cooked with the curry paste? Now that’s magical. Studded with sweet rich currants, fresh coriander and roasted cauliflower, this rice dish packs flavour in every bite, with a dollop of creamy Greek yoghurt for a tangy contrast.
